node_2.subject: Isabella Rodriguez
node_2.description: This is Isabella Rodriguez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 6:00 am, go to Hobbs Cafe and open at 8:00 am, work at the counter until 3:00 pm, taking breaks as needed, spend time ordering party materials and decorations for the Valentine's Day party, close the cafe at 8:00 pm, go home and have dinner.
